{"tid":978104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張 學 友 開 個 唱 暗 諷 填 海 華 是 廢 老","createTime":"2019-01-11T15:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T19:05:18.000Z","uid":215823,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9846af5800124b2f5b2cdf97f1f2b9024a8f6e80","tid":978104,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"張學友唱完《不經不覺》、《春風秋雨》再唱《你的名字我的姓氏》，揀番之前影觀眾錫嗰一對出嚟，咁啱今日呢位女觀眾生日，學友即場唱英文生日歌。學友又送咗一幅當時兩人錫嘅相做禮物，又寫上祝福語同簽名。學友話同團隊出咗120分力：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「估唔到自己就快6張嘢（60歲），仲諗做唔做到，嚟到219場，證明我係得嘅。」</span></span></strong>之後唱《愛是永恆》同《祝福》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJ1xw0j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJ1xw0j.png&h=0b41b57d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HxXH61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HxXH61.png&h=99c2b25d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebf970fc1ba81a8e54f7bdbdbd9ffcb1b451e178","tid":978104,"uid":15880,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:19:44.000Z","msg":"個rundown 仲係同2016 一樣"},{"pid":"ecf40c05db9425161949e37f4cfdd0cc2d1d2b15","tid":978104,"uid":132587,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:22:36.000Z","msg":"輸曬d錢有得唔番工咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b69aca4bcc7a8db029db4a1ac07bd9a9892fea","tid":978104,"uid":3962,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"話唔係填氹都唔信<br />\n正常以佢成世人賺到嘅錢洗乜開到咁密除非投資失利"},{"pid":"f4ce02193e1d0ebcd8ad48c90af57d2a422cede0","tid":978104,"uid":129273,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"05b69aca4bcc7a8db029db4a1ac07bd9a9892fea","tid":978104,"uid":3962,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"話唔係填氹都唔信<br />\n正常以佢成世人賺到嘅錢洗乜開到咁密除非投資失利"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T18:37:43.000Z","msg":"劇聞佢老婆好撚癲,怪獸家長又重